{
    "verses": [
        {
            "id": 1873,
            "verse_number": 71,
            "verse_key": "15:71",
            "hizb_number": 27,
            "rub_el_hizb_number": 106,
            "ruku_number": 222,
            "manzil_number": 3,
            "sajdah_number": null,
            "text_uthmani": "قَالَ هَـٰٓؤُلَآءِ بَنَاتِىٓ إِن كُنتُمْ فَـٰعِلِينَ",
            "page_number": 266,
            "juz_number": 14,
            "translations": [
                {
                    "id": 96774,
                    "resource_id": 20,
                    "text": "[Lot] said, \"These are my daughters<sup foot_note=196596>1</sup> - if you would be doers [of lawful marriage].\""
                },
                {
                    "id": 220746,
                    "resource_id": 39,
                    "text": "Nabi Lut berkata: \"Di sini ada anak-anak perempuanku, kalaulah kamu mahu melakukan (secara halal)."
                },
                {
                    "id": 1092850,
                    "resource_id": 161,
                    "text": "(লূত (আ.)) বলল, ‘তোমরা যদি কিছু করতেই চাও তাহলে এই আমার (জাতির) কন্যারা আছে।’"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": 1874,
            "verse_number": 72,
            "verse_key": "15:72",
            "hizb_number": 27,
            "rub_el_hizb_number": 106,
            "ruku_number": 222,
            "manzil_number": 3,
            "sajdah_number": null,
            "text_uthmani": "لَعَمْرُكَ إِنَّهُمْ لَفِى سَكْرَتِهِمْ يَعْمَهُونَ",
            "page_number": 266,
            "juz_number": 14,
            "translations": [
                {
                    "id": 96775,
                    "resource_id": 20,
                    "text": "By your life, [O Muḥammad], indeed they were, in their intoxication, wandering blindly."
                },
                {
                    "id": 220744,
                    "resource_id": 39,
                    "text": "Demi umurmu (wahai Muhammad), sesungguhnya mereka membuta tuli dalam kemabukan maksiat mereka."
                },
                {
                    "id": 1092851,
                    "resource_id": 161,
                    "text": "তোমার জীবনের শপথ হে নাবী! তারা উন্মত্ত নেশায় আত্মহারা হয়ে পড়েছিল।"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": 1875,
            "verse_number": 73,
            "verse_key": "15:73",
            "hizb_number": 27,
            "rub_el_hizb_number": 106,
            "ruku_number": 222,
            "manzil_number": 3,
            "sajdah_number": null,
            "text_uthmani": "فَأَخَذَتْهُمُ ٱلصَّيْحَةُ مُشْرِقِينَ",
            "page_number": 266,
            "juz_number": 14,
            "translations": [
                {
                    "id": 96776,
                    "resource_id": 20,
                    "text": "So the shriek<sup foot_note=196597>1</sup> seized them at sunrise."
                },
                {
                    "id": 220743,
                    "resource_id": 39,
                    "text": "Akhirnya merekapun dibinasakan oleh letusan suara yang menggempakan bumi, ketika matahari terbit."
                },
                {
                    "id": 1092852,
                    "resource_id": 161,
                    "text": "সূর্যোদয়ের সময়ে এক প্রচন্ড ধ্বনি তাদের উপর আঘাত হানল।"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": 1876,
            "verse_number": 74,
            "verse_key": "15:74",
            "hizb_number": 27,
            "rub_el_hizb_number": 106,
            "ruku_number": 222,
            "manzil_number": 3,
            "sajdah_number": null,
            "text_uthmani": "فَجَعَلْنَا عَـٰلِيَهَا سَافِلَهَا وَأَمْطَرْنَا عَلَيْهِمْ حِجَارَةً مِّن سِجِّيلٍ",
            "page_number": 266,
            "juz_number": 14,
            "translations": [
                {
                    "id": 96777,
                    "resource_id": 20,
                    "text": "And We made the highest part [of the city] its lowest and rained upon them stones of hard clay."
                },
                {
                    "id": 220749,
                    "resource_id": 39,
                    "text": "Maka Kami jadikan negeri kaum Lut itu tunggang-balik (tertimbus segala yang ada di muka buminya), dan kami hujani atasnya dengan batu dari tanah yang dibakar."
                },
                {
                    "id": 1092853,
                    "resource_id": 161,
                    "text": "আর আমি সে জনপদকে উল্টে (উপর-নীচ) করে দিলাম আর তাদের উপর পাকানো মাটির প্রস্তর বর্ষণ করলাম।"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": 1877,
            "verse_number": 75,
            "verse_key": "15:75",
            "hizb_number": 27,
            "rub_el_hizb_number": 106,
            "ruku_number": 222,
            "manzil_number": 3,
            "sajdah_number": null,
            "text_uthmani": "إِنَّ فِى ذَٰلِكَ لَـَٔايَـٰتٍ لِّلْمُتَوَسِّمِينَ",
            "page_number": 266,
            "juz_number": 14,
            "translations": [
                {
                    "id": 96778,
                    "resource_id": 20,
                    "text": "Indeed in that are signs for those who discern."
                },
                {
                    "id": 220748,
                    "resource_id": 39,
                    "text": "Sesungguhnya balasan azab yang demikian itu, mengandungi tanda-tanda bagi orang-orang yang kenalkan sesuatu serta memerhati dan memikirkannya."
                },
                {
                    "id": 1092854,
                    "resource_id": 161,
                    "text": "এতে অবশ্যই অন্তর্দৃষ্টিসম্পন্ন লোকেদের জন্য অনেক নিদর্শন রয়েছে।"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": 1878,
            "verse_number": 76,
            "verse_key": "15:76",
            "hizb_number": 27,
            "rub_el_hizb_number": 106,
            "ruku_number": 222,
            "manzil_number": 3,
            "sajdah_number": null,
            "text_uthmani": "وَإِنَّهَا لَبِسَبِيلٍ مُّقِيمٍ",
            "page_number": 266,
            "juz_number": 14,
            "translations": [
                {
                    "id": 96779,
                    "resource_id": 20,
                    "text": "And indeed, they [i.e., those cities] are [situated] on an established road."
                },
                {
                    "id": 220750,
                    "resource_id": 39,
                    "text": "Dan sesungguhnya negeri kaum Lut yang telah dibinasakan itu, terletak di jalan yang tetap (dilalui orang)."
                },
                {
                    "id": 1092855,
                    "resource_id": 161,
                    "text": "এটি মানুষের চলাচল পথের পাশেই বিদ্যমান।"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": 1879,
            "verse_number": 77,
            "verse_key": "15:77",
            "hizb_number": 27,
            "rub_el_hizb_number": 106,
            "ruku_number": 222,
            "manzil_number": 3,
            "sajdah_number": null,
            "text_uthmani": "إِنَّ فِى ذَٰلِكَ لَـَٔايَةً لِّلْمُؤْمِنِينَ",
            "page_number": 266,
            "juz_number": 14,
            "translations": [
                {
                    "id": 96780,
                    "resource_id": 20,
                    "text": "Indeed in that is a sign for the believers."
                },
                {
                    "id": 220769,
                    "resource_id": 39,
                    "text": "Sesungguhnya keadaan yang demikian, mengandungi satu tanda yang memberi kesedaran kepada orang-orang yang beriman."
                },
                {
                    "id": 1092856,
                    "resource_id": 161,
                    "text": "মু’মিনদের জন্য এতে বড়ই নিদর্শন রয়েছে।"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": 1880,
            "verse_number": 78,
            "verse_key": "15:78",
            "hizb_number": 27,
            "rub_el_hizb_number": 106,
            "ruku_number": 222,
            "manzil_number": 3,
            "sajdah_number": null,
            "text_uthmani": "وَإِن كَانَ أَصْحَـٰبُ ٱلْأَيْكَةِ لَظَـٰلِمِينَ",
            "page_number": 266,
            "juz_number": 14,
            "translations": [
                {
                    "id": 96781,
                    "resource_id": 20,
                    "text": "And the companions of the thicket [i.e., the people of Madyan] were [also] wrongdoers,"
                },
                {
                    "id": 220747,
                    "resource_id": 39,
                    "text": "Dan sebenarnya penduduk kampung \"Aikah\" adalah orang-orang yang berlaku zalim."
                },
                {
                    "id": 1092857,
                    "resource_id": 161,
                    "text": "আর আয়কাহবাসীরাও অবশ্যই যালিম ছিল।"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": 1881,
            "verse_number": 79,
            "verse_key": "15:79",
            "hizb_number": 27,
            "rub_el_hizb_number": 106,
            "ruku_number": 222,
            "manzil_number": 3,
            "sajdah_number": null,
            "text_uthmani": "فَٱنتَقَمْنَا مِنْهُمْ وَإِنَّهُمَا لَبِإِمَامٍ مُّبِينٍ",
            "page_number": 266,
            "juz_number": 14,
            "translations": [
                {
                    "id": 96782,
                    "resource_id": 20,
                    "text": "So We took retribution from them, and indeed, both [cities] are on a clear highway."
                },
                {
                    "id": 220742,
                    "resource_id": 39,
                    "text": "Maka Kami membalas kezaliman mereka itu dengan azab yang membinasakan; dan sesungguhnya kedua-duanya itu terletak di jalan yang terang (yang masih dilalui orang)."
                },
                {
                    "id": 1092858,
                    "resource_id": 161,
                    "text": "কাজেই তাদের উপর প্রতিশোধ নিয়েছিলাম, এ দু’টো জনপদই প্রকাশ্য পথের উপর অবস্থিত।"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": 1882,
            "verse_number": 80,
            "verse_key": "15:80",
            "hizb_number": 27,
            "rub_el_hizb_number": 106,
            "ruku_number": 223,
            "manzil_number": 3,
            "sajdah_number": null,
            "text_uthmani": "وَلَقَدْ كَذَّبَ أَصْحَـٰبُ ٱلْحِجْرِ ٱلْمُرْسَلِينَ",
            "page_number": 266,
            "juz_number": 14,
            "translations": [
                {
                    "id": 96784,
                    "resource_id": 20,
                    "text": "And certainly did the companions of al-Ḥijr<sup foot_note=196598>1</sup> [i.e., the Thamūd] deny the messengers."
                },
                {
                    "id": 220756,
                    "resource_id": 39,
                    "text": "Dan demi sesungguhnya penduduk \"Al-Hijr\" telah mendustakan Rasul-rasul."
                },
                {
                    "id": 1092859,
                    "resource_id": 161,
                    "text": "হিজর-এর লোকেরাও রসূলদেরকে অমান্য করেছিল।"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": 1883,
            "verse_number": 81,
            "verse_key": "15:81",
            "hizb_number": 27,
            "rub_el_hizb_number": 106,
            "ruku_number": 223,
            "manzil_number": 3,
            "sajdah_number": null,
            "text_uthmani": "وَءَاتَيْنَـٰهُمْ ءَايَـٰتِنَا فَكَانُوا۟ عَنْهَا مُعْرِضِينَ",
            "page_number": 266,
            "juz_number": 14,
            "translations": [
                {
                    "id": 96785,
                    "resource_id": 20,
                    "text": "And We gave them Our signs, but from them they were turning away."
                },
                {
                    "id": 220755,
                    "resource_id": 39,
                    "text": "Dan Kami telah berikan kepada mereka tanda-tanda (yang membuktikan kebenaran ugama dan Rasul Kami); dalam pada itu, mereka terus juga berpaling (mengingkarinya)."
                },
                {
                    "id": 1092860,
                    "resource_id": 161,
                    "text": "আমি তাদেরকে আমার নিদর্শনাবলী দিয়েছিলাম কিন্তু তাত্থেকে তারা মুখ ফিরিয়েই রেখেছিল।"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": 1884,
            "verse_number": 82,
            "verse_key": "15:82",
            "hizb_number": 27,
            "rub_el_hizb_number": 106,
            "ruku_number": 223,
            "manzil_number": 3,
            "sajdah_number": null,
            "text_uthmani": "وَكَانُوا۟ يَنْحِتُونَ مِنَ ٱلْجِبَالِ بُيُوتًا ءَامِنِينَ",
            "page_number": 266,
            "juz_number": 14,
            "translations": [
                {
                    "id": 96786,
                    "resource_id": 20,
                    "text": "And they used to carve from the mountains, houses, feeling secure."
                },
                {
                    "id": 220757,
                    "resource_id": 39,
                    "text": "Dan mereka memahat sebahagian dari gunung-ganang, sebagai tempat tinggal dengan keadaan aman (dari sesuatu bahaya)."
                },
                {
                    "id": 1092861,
                    "resource_id": 161,
                    "text": "তারা পাহাড় খোদাই করতঃ ঘর তৈরি করে নিজেদেরকে নিরাপদ ভাবত।"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": 1885,
            "verse_number": 83,
            "verse_key": "15:83",
            "hizb_number": 27,
            "rub_el_hizb_number": 106,
            "ruku_number": 223,
            "manzil_number": 3,
            "sajdah_number": null,
            "text_uthmani": "فَأَخَذَتْهُمُ ٱلصَّيْحَةُ مُصْبِحِينَ",
            "page_number": 266,
            "juz_number": 14,
            "translations": [
                {
                    "id": 96787,
                    "resource_id": 20,
                    "text": "But the shriek seized them at early morning,"
                },
                {
                    "id": 220753,
                    "resource_id": 39,
                    "text": "Meskipun demikian, mereka dibinasakan juga oleh letusan suara yang menggempakan pada bumi waktu pagi."
                },
                {
                    "id": 1092862,
                    "resource_id": 161,
                    "text": "অতঃপর এক সকালে প্রচন্ড ধ্বনি তাদের উপর আঘাত হানল।"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": 1886,
            "verse_number": 84,
            "verse_key": "15:84",
            "hizb_number": 27,
            "rub_el_hizb_number": 106,
            "ruku_number": 223,
            "manzil_number": 3,
            "sajdah_number": null,
            "text_uthmani": "فَمَآ أَغْنَىٰ عَنْهُم مَّا كَانُوا۟ يَكْسِبُونَ",
            "page_number": 266,
            "juz_number": 14,
            "translations": [
                {
                    "id": 96788,
                    "resource_id": 20,
                    "text": "So nothing availed them [from] what they used to earn."
                },
                {
                    "id": 220760,
                    "resource_id": 39,
                    "text": "Maka apa yang mereka telah usahakan itu, tidak dapat menolong mereka sedikit pun."
                },
                {
                    "id": 1092863,
                    "resource_id": 161,
                    "text": "তাদের উপার্জন তাদের কোন কাজে আসল না।"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": 1887,
            "verse_number": 85,
            "verse_key": "15:85",
            "hizb_number": 27,
            "rub_el_hizb_number": 106,
            "ruku_number": 223,
            "manzil_number": 3,
            "sajdah_number": null,
            "text_uthmani": "وَمَا خَلَقْنَا ٱلسَّمَـٰوَٰتِ وَٱلْأَرْضَ وَمَا بَيْنَهُمَآ إِلَّا بِٱلْحَقِّ ۗ وَإِنَّ ٱلسَّاعَةَ لَـَٔاتِيَةٌ ۖ فَٱصْفَحِ ٱلصَّفْحَ ٱلْجَمِيلَ",
            "page_number": 266,
            "juz_number": 14,
            "translations": [
                {
                    "id": 96789,
                    "resource_id": 20,
                    "text": "And We have not created the heavens and earth and that between them except in truth. And indeed, the Hour is coming; so forgive with gracious forgiveness."
                },
                {
                    "id": 220759,
                    "resource_id": 39,
                    "text": "Dan (ingatlah) tiadalah Kami mencipta langit dan bumi serta segala yang ada di antara keduanya itu, melainkan dengan cara yang sungguh layak dan berhikmat; dan sesungguhnya hari kiamat itu tetap akan datang; oleh itu biarkanlah (golongan kafir yang mendustakanmu itu wahai Muhammad) serta layanlah mereka dengan cara yang elok."
                },
                {
                    "id": 1092864,
                    "resource_id": 161,
                    "text": "আমি আসমানসমূহ, যমীন আর এ দু’য়ের মাঝে যা কিছু আছে প্রকৃত উদ্দেশ্য ছাড়া সৃষ্টি করিনি। ক্বিয়ামাত অবশ্যই আসবে, কাজেই উত্তম পন্থায় (তাদেরকে) এড়িয়ে যাও।"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": 1888,
            "verse_number": 86,
            "verse_key": "15:86",
            "hizb_number": 27,
            "rub_el_hizb_number": 106,
            "ruku_number": 223,
            "manzil_number": 3,
            "sajdah_number": null,
            "text_uthmani": "إِنَّ رَبَّكَ هُوَ ٱلْخَلَّـٰقُ ٱلْعَلِيمُ",
            "page_number": 266,
            "juz_number": 14,
            "translations": [
                {
                    "id": 96790,
                    "resource_id": 20,
                    "text": "Indeed, your Lord - He is the Knowing Creator."
                },
                {
                    "id": 220758,
                    "resource_id": 39,
                    "text": "Sesungguhnya Tuhanmu, Dia lah yang menciptakan sekalian makhluk, lagi Yang Maha Mengetahui (akan hal mereka)."
                },
                {
                    "id": 1092865,
                    "resource_id": 161,
                    "text": "নিশ্চয় তোমার প্রতিপালক তিনি সর্বস্রষ্টা, সর্বজ্ঞ।"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": 1889,
            "verse_number": 87,
            "verse_key": "15:87",
            "hizb_number": 27,
            "rub_el_hizb_number": 106,
            "ruku_number": 223,
            "manzil_number": 3,
            "sajdah_number": null,
            "text_uthmani": "وَلَقَدْ ءَاتَيْنَـٰكَ سَبْعًا مِّنَ ٱلْمَثَانِى وَٱلْقُرْءَانَ ٱلْعَظِيمَ",
            "page_number": 266,
            "juz_number": 14,
            "translations": [
                {
                    "id": 96791,
                    "resource_id": 20,
                    "text": "And We have certainly given you, [O Muḥammad], seven of the often repeated [verses]<sup foot_note=196599>1</sup> and the great Qur’ān."
                },
                {
                    "id": 220761,
                    "resource_id": 39,
                    "text": "Dan sesungguhnya Kami telah memberi kepadamu (wahai Muhammad) tujuh ayat yang diulang-ulang bacaannya dan seluruh Al-Quran yang amat besar kemuliaan dan faedahnya."
                },
                {
                    "id": 1092866,
                    "resource_id": 161,
                    "text": "আমি তোমাকে দিয়েছি পুনঃ পুনঃ আবৃত্ত সপ্ত আয়াত আর মহা কুরআন।"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": 1890,
            "verse_number": 88,
